320g broccoli , to serve|1
STEP 2Add the chicken and stir-fry until it begins to colour, then tip in the tomatoes, squeeze in some tomato pure and add the bouillon and 150ml water. Cover and simmer for 10 mins.|0
Add the chicken and stir-fry until it begins to colour, then tip in the tomatoes, squeeze in some tomato pure and add the bouillon and 150ml water. Cover and simmer for 10 mins.|0
Add the chicken and stir-fry until it begins to colour, then tip in the tomatoes, squeeze in some tomato pure and add the bouillon and 150ml water. Cover and simmer for 10 mins.|0
STEP 3Mix the peanut butter with 100ml water, then stir into the stew and cook for 5 mins more. Spoon the mixture equally into two 24 x 18cm shallow pie dishes.|0
